================================================================================
DATA SOURCE: Metropolitan Transportation Authority (MTA)
================================================================================

The Momentarily publisher fetches data from MTA-operated APIs at
https://api.mta.info, including:

  - GTFS-Realtime Service Alerts (subway, LIRR, MNR, bus)
  - NYCT elevator and escalator availability feeds
  - GTFS static schedules and route metadata

All such data is the property of the Metropolitan Transportation Authority.
Use of MTA data is governed by the MTA developer agreement, which is separate
from and not superseded by the Apache 2.0 license that covers the publisher code:

  https://api.mta.info/#/DataFeedAgreement

